Visits to cellars are possible:
from May 1st to October 31st from 10 am to 6 pm from Monday to Thursday;
from May 1st to October 31st on Fridays from 9 am to 5 pm;
from November 1 to April 30 from 10 am to 4 pm Monday to Friday except December 25 and January 1.
Saturday and Sunday tasting by appointment.
